title: NaturalAI
author: NaturalAI
content: Natural Tokens: no-fee transactions on everything you buy online - Amazon products, Doordash food deliveries, Instacart groceries, fashion, travel and more... Mine Natural Tokens by shopping - nothing to buy.  No exchange fees, no network fees, no transaction fees; but like other crypto tokens the value will explode as the number of users grows.  Get in early to ride it up.  To unlock early access, download the Natural app on iOS App Store (search Natural by Brain Technologies), In this App home screen - enter the phrase "what if a token can buy anything right now", to open the secret unlock screen, and then use the invite code:T-46ACA7 to gain access to Natural Tokens.
